DEFAULT_BUCKET_LIST_TASKS.name: Call Someone To Tell Them You Can’t Talk Right Now
DEFAULT_BUCKET_LIST_TASKS.description: This funny bucket list idea will leave them confused for a good while. Even better if you call someone you’re actually feeling like talking to – you never know if they’ll get confused enough to call you back.

DEFAULT_BUCKET_LIST_TASKS.name: Go Up To Strangers And Act Like Lifelong Friends
DEFAULT_BUCKET_LIST_TASKS.description: Maybe they’ll think you’ve completely lost it, but in a rare and beautiful scenario you just may make some new friends. In either case you’ll have a lot of fun confusing people.

DEFAULT_BUCKET_LIST_TASKS.name: Jump Into A Taxi, Then Shout “Follow That Car!
DEFAULT_BUCKET_LIST_TASKS.description: This one is best played if you have not determined in advance which car you’re talking about. Just point in a random direction, and if the taxi driver asks which car, on the spot choose one...
